metadata.name: PizzaDogz #1
metadata.description: PizzaDogz is a collection of 10,000 unique NFTs whose purpose is to make a lasting difference in this world. This is accomplished through donations to meaningful and impactful charities. 15% of all mint sales will be donated to the ASPCA and Feeding America. 10% of all royalties generated by your trading of PizzaDogz will go to charities of PizzaDogz holders choosing EVERY MONTH!!! Help with this ongoing project and join us in making a difference ONE SLICE AT A TIME!!
